*Trik* je bio potpuno neočekivan. (The trick was completely unexpected.)

*Trikom* je sprečio padao. (He prevented the fall with a trick.)

Moj je kum bio majstor u *trikovima*. (My godfather was a master of tricks.)

On je često prakticirao *trikove*. (He often practiced tricks.)

Otkrivanje *trika* je bilo zaista zanimljivo. (Revealing the trick was really interesting.)

Moj sin se igrao *trika*. (My son was playing tricks.)